    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "okay i get the formula now. but it still feels so predatory, like the system is designed so you're always fighting an uphill battle. it's almost like there's something working in the background to stop the balance from dropping. is there any way to calculate exactly how much longer it'll take if i just stick to the minimums vs if i try to throw an extra $50 or $100 at the principal each month?",
